          (infrequent <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">consumers</ENAMEX> cohort, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">n</ENAMEX> = <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1274</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">households</ENAMEX>;
          <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">approximately 65%</NUMEX> response rate). <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Participants</ENAMEX> in the
