          the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Wisconsin State Laboratory of Hygiene</ENAMEX> was <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">0.25</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">ng</ENAMEX>/mL.
          <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">Only 1</NUMEX> of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">350</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">samples</ENAMEX> was below this limit, and it was
